All this being said, however, I do have some concerns. 

Namely, wouldn't the Coalition and the World Parahealth Organization be opposed to this? If this project were to spread to unauthorized third parties, we could be looking at a potential second Impasse. Make no mistake, I am eager to work on this project, but I do not wish for what happened 27 years ago to repeat.

